<div class="title">Before Mixing, Be Informed</div>
<div class="substance">Bupropion (Wellbutrin), Alcohol, Cocaine, Ecstasy, Cannabis & Adderall</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=over+user&Exact=1">over user</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; over user. "Before Mixing, Be Informed: An Experience with Bupropion (Wellbutrin), Alcohol, Cocaine, Ecstasy, Cannabis & Adderall (exp29219)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 15, 2003. erowid.org/exp/29219</div>

